1- Make sure that you are using perl 5.8.8 or better
2- Make sure that you can resolve these dependencies:
    use Getopt::Long;
    use Net::Telnet;
    use Data::Dumper;
    use FileHandle;
    use threads;
    use threads::shared;
    use Thread::Queue;

3- copy 
   etc/xinit.d/webnoded 
   usr/local/bin/webnoded.pl

to each of your varnish hosts and restart xinet.

4- copy
   usr/local/bin/watch-varnish.pl

to your admin host
